item.title: Episode 19 (The Techno Edition Renegade Sessions)
item.description: Something a little different from the shranz type of stuff I've been playing recently, really like this live mix that I put together for this radio broadcast. This one goes all over the place from mml to techno to tech hose all the way to some disco house type stuff but keeping that robotic energy that I like, hope you guys enjoy as I've had fun doing this broadcast. ez you can peep out my archives @ http://tech-noid.net/
